title: [PSP]WWE SmackDown vs. Raw 2011[ENG][FULL]
description:
WWE SmackDown vs. Raw 2011

Tested and working on PSP-1000 (5.50 GEN-D3) and PSP-2000 (5.50 GEN-D3).

Unpacked filesize: 1.34 GB

Instructions:

Extract game-iso from archive to ISO directory on your Memory Stick. This can be done using WinRAR or Total Commander.

ATTENTION! In order to play the game you have to set 'UMD ISO MODE' to 'M33 driver'

and 'CPU SPEED GAME' to 'Default'. Like that:
 <a href="
http://img842.imageshack.us/img842/3627/20101027005604.png" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://img842.imageshack.us/img842/3627/20101027005604.png</a>

And remember these files are for the custom firmwares ONLY!
